          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>basa strips</strong> and cook for 3-4 min on each side or until crisp and cooked through – these are your <strong>crispy fish fingers</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
