      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>dill</strong> finely</p><p>Combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong> with the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped dill </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>dill mayo</strong></p>",
